CustomField.formula: IF( Timestamp_Documents_Out__c - Timestamp_Documents_Requested__c> 0 , TEXT( FLOOR( Timestamp_Documents_Out__c - Timestamp_Documents_Requested__c) ) & " days " & TEXT( FLOOR( MOD( (Timestamp_Documents_Out__c - Timestamp_Documents_Requested__c) * 24, 24 ) ) ) & " hours " & TEXT( ROUND( MOD( (Timestamp_Documents_Out__c - Timestamp_Documents_Requested__c) * 24 * 60, 60 ), 0 ) ) & " minutes", "" )
CustomField.label: Request Documents to Documents Out
